Unnamed: 0: 1 x AX5000 (enabled) without DC linkILCtotal = ILCvar + ILCfix
2 x AX5000 (not enabled) in DC linkIABtotal = IABfix_1 + IABfix_2

1 x AX5000 (enabled) + 1 x AX5000 (not enabled) in DC linkIABtotal = IABvar_1 + IABfix_1 + IABfix_2If the AX5000_2 is also enabled the equation is as follows:IABtotal = IABvar_1 + IABvar_2 + IABfix_1 + IABfix_2
